@startuml startup
title RAMA Startup Sequence

start

:Detect PR creation or synchronization;
:Trigger GitHub Actions workflow;
:Import, build, and execute RAMA;
:Load rama.json configuration file;

if (Is rama.json empty?) then (yes)
  :Use default configuration;
  :Set model/metamodel extensions to .model/.ecore;
  :Use Ecore metamodel from EMF;
else (no)
  :Determine file extensions and metamodels to use;
endif

:Fetch affected model/metamodel files from GitHub API;
:Analyze each affected file → <pr-model-file-cases-all.puml>;

stop
@enduml